			<CASNumber>7775-27-1</CASNumber>
			<common:generalComment xml:lang="en">Sodium persulfate is a strong oxidizer and a severe irritant of skin, eyes, and respiratory system. It is almost non-hygroscopic and has particularly good ability to be stored for a long time. It is easy and safe to handle, and it is not combustible, but releases oxygen easily and assists combustion of other materials. It is used for R&amp;D and has applications in in situ chemical oxidation (ISCO) for the remediation of contaminated groundwater and soil.</common:generalComment>
			<common:generalComment xml:lang="zh">过硫酸钠是一种强氧化剂，对皮肤、眼睛和呼吸系统具有严重刺激性。它几乎不吸湿，并且具有特别好的长期储存能力。它易于操作且安全，不可燃，但易于释放氧气并有助于其他材料的燃烧。它用于研发，并在原位化学氧化（ISCO）中应用，用于修复受污染的地下水和土壤。</common:generalComment>
			<sumFormula>Na2S2O8</sumFormula>
